column5: Went out to a pal's hut. Did good. A 14 inch perch too! Yeehaw!! Also lost a screamer that cut the line. Maybe a big eye or trout.
Very nice fish! Great report and pics!!!
Huge pike maybe?  nice perch too
nice fish, and congrats on monster perch...
way to go....thats some good eating,great report and pics,  cheers
Nice perch. Those whities are a good meal to.
nice perch u should put that on ofah awards wondering if you smoke your whities suppose to be very good
Nice report... Thats definately one huge perch and nice whitie too...
Looks like a great day you had.  What a honkin perch that is.  Woohooo.  Great report.  Joey
Yum Yum ...  how'd they taste ?    Looks like a great day. That perch may be pushing 14 1/4.  Huge !
So, Who caught the fish. really you can tell me.  Good going Chris.
Very nice Chris, glad you still had some ice down there to get out.  Looks like you are warming your hands though,   , or are you rubbing them together, imagining the feast ahead???
Tom...look at the post date for Chris's original post. Clamp-it's either playin or asleep at the switch today ! LOL

SOOOOO............................ are you saying I am slow on the uptake Wayne, watcha trying to tell me,  YUP, the first statement says it all,    as I saw the "ice firming up again" statement, and we just went through that. Didn't notice the date of the post whatsoever.
Well done nice sized perch and white you have there thanks for sharing   cheers
